{"word":"G2742 - καύσων - kaúsōn - kow'-sone - Heat","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καύσων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kaúsōn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kow'-sone"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Heat"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"உஷ்ணம், கடும்வெயில், ஈரஸ் என்னும் கிழக்குக்காற்று - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. burning heat of the sun"},{"paragraph":"2. Eurus, a very dry, hot, east wind, scorching and drying up everything"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2741 - καυσόω - kausóō - kow-so'-o/2741\">G2741</a>; a <i>glare:</i> - (burning) heat."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2740 - καῦσις - kaûsis - kow'-sis/2740\">G2740</a>, <a href=\"#/G2741 - καυσόω - kausóō - kow-so'-o/2741\">G2741</a>, <a href=\"#/G2742 - καύσων - kaúsōn - kow'-sone/2742\">G2742</a>, <a href=\"#/G2743 - καυτηριάζω - kautēriázō - kow-tay-ree-ad'-zo/2743\">G2743</a>"}]}